{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, various optimization algorithms have been incorporated into the convolutional neural network model, and the performance has been continuously improved.",
    "For example, batch normalization (BN) techniques can keep the inputs of layers more evenly distributed.",
    "Dropout technology can refine the network, effectively reduce overfitting, and achieve a certain degree of regularization.",
    "The ReLU function can accelerate the convergence of stochastic gradient descent [59].",
    "Data augmentation (DA) technology can effectively expand the dataset and help alleviate overfitting [60].CNN is typically utilized for processing array-like data."
  ]
}